#. <section class="sutta" id="sn46.42"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn46.42:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.42:0.2"
msgid "5. Cakkavattivagga"
msgstr "5. A Wheel Turning Monarch"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn46.42:0.3"
msgid "42. Cakkavattisutta"
msgstr "42. A Wheel Turning Monarch"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.99"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.42:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Rañño, bhikkhave, cakkavattissa pātubhāvā sattannaṃ ratanānaṃ pātubhāvo "
"hoti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when a Wheel Turning Monarch appears seven treasures appear."

msgctxt "sn46.42:1.2"
msgid "Katamesaṃ sattannaṃ?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "sn46.42:1.3"
msgid ""
"Cakkaratanassa pātubhāvo hoti, hatthiratanassa pātubhāvo hoti, assaratanassa "
"pātubhāvo hoti, maṇiratanassa pātubhāvo hoti, itthiratanassa pātubhāvo hoti, "
"gahapatiratanassa pātubhāvo hoti, pariṇāyakaratanassa pātubhāvo hoti."
msgstr ""
"The wheel, the elephant, the horse, the jewel, the woman, the treasurer, and "
"the counselor."

msgctxt "sn46.42:1.4"
msgid ""
"Rañño, bhikkhave, cakkavattissa pātubhāvā imesaṃ sattannaṃ ratanānaṃ "
"pātubhāvo hoti."
msgstr "When a Wheel Turning Monarch appears these seven treasures appear."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.42:2.1"
msgid ""
"Tathāgatassa, bhikkhave, pātubhāvā arahato sammāsambuddhassa sattannaṃ "
"bojjhaṅgaratanānaṃ pātubhāvo hoti."
msgstr ""
"When a Realized One, a perfected one, a fully awakened Buddha appears the "
"seven treasures of the awakening factors appear."

msgctxt "sn46.42:2.2"
msgid "Katamesaṃ sattannaṃ?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "sn46.42:2.3"
msgid ""
"Satisambojjhaṅgassa ratanassa pātubhāvo hoti … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgassa "
"ratanassa pātubhāvo hoti."
msgstr ""
"The treasures of the awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of "
"principles, energy, rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity."

msgctxt "sn46.42:2.4"
msgid ""
"Tathāgatassa, bhikkhave, pātubhāvā arahato sammāsambuddhassa imesaṃ "
"sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgaratanānaṃ pātubhāvo hotī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When a Realized One, a perfected one, a fully awakened Buddha appears these "
"seven treasures of the awakening factors appear.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.42:2.5"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
